      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.194 - The Prophet (sw) said:\n‘Indeed, Sayyida Fatimah Al-Zahra {S.A} is not like any of you; She does not experience menstrual blood or postnatal bleeding, like the heavenly maidens.'"
